headline: What Catalysts Are Shaping the Changing Story for Uber Technologies?
summary: Uber Technologies has seen its fair value estimate nudged upward, now rising from $108.88 to $110.55. This revision comes amid ongoing analyst debate. Bullish perspectives highlight improved core fundamentals and platform momentum, while some concerns remain about growth pace and evolving profitability guidance.
